[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0352","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0352.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0736","title":"Microsoft IIS 及 Site Server showcode.asp 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"IIS 和 Site Server 中的 showcode.asp 示例文件存在任意文件读取漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过特制的 HTTP 请求利用该示例脚本读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Microsoft IIS 4.0 和 Site Server 3.0 等版本，攻击者只需向目标服务器发送构造的 URL 即可触发，利用门槛较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0736"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.020","remediation":"立即删除 IIS 4.0 或 Site Server 3.0 服务器上的 showcode.asp、viewcode.asp、code.asp、codebrws.asp 等示例文件查看器脚本，这些文件默认可被远程攻击者利用读取任意文件。生产环境禁止部署任何 IIS 示例文件，同时安装 MS99-013 补丁程序。如无法立即删除，可通过 NTFS 权限限制对上述脚本的读取访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A932","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19129","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0736.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0736.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0736","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0736.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0736.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mjqv-8fmv-523x/GHSA-mjqv-8fmv-523x.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0736.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/ShowCode.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0736.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0352.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0352.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0352.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0355","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0355.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0737","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 showcode.asp 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 默认安装附带 showcode.asp 示例脚本，该脚本未对用户输入的文件路径参数进行充分过滤，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向服务器发送特制 HTTP 请求，利用该脚本读取服务器上的任意文件内容（如系统配置文件、脚本源码等），导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 及 Site Server 相关版本，攻击条件低，仅需目标开放 Web 服务即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0737"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.140","remediation":"删除 IIS 安装目录下的 `IISSamples` 虚拟目录及 `showcode.asp` 文件（默认路径 `C:\\Inetpub\\IISSamples\\`），并移除 `/IISsamples` 映射。如业务需要保留示例脚本，应通过 NTFS 权限限制仅管理员可访问。建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 以上版本，新版 IIS 已移除这些有风险的示例文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0737.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0737","https://github.com/GuangrenYu/WangYi/blob/db7e4b8b6d2f1d5bfd5908a02b4b5fcac6b3880d/poc_kb/custom/1999/CVE-1999-0737.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0737.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mrf7-29w2-32h3/GHSA-mrf7-29w2-32h3.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0737.yaml","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/iis_viewcode.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/ivanitlearning/CTF-Repos/blob/b5364388a861fc7457409d494a9d075d73e7867e/Vulnhub/SkyTower/Web-scan.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0737.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0355.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0356","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0356.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0738","title":"Microsoft IIS 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"IIS 和 Site Server 中的 code.asp 示例文件存在任意文件读取漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可利用该示例文件的参数读取服务器上的任意文件，包括系统配置文件、源代码等敏感信息。该漏洞影响早期版本的 Microsoft IIS 和 Site Server，攻击门槛低，危害较大。官方推荐删除或禁用 code.asp 示例文件以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0738"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.270","remediation":"删除 IIS 默认安装的示例文件 %SystemRoot%\\Help\\iis\\htm\\core\\code.asp，或安装微软 1999 年发布的相关安全更新。临时的缓解措施是通过 IIS 管理器移除 \"IIS Samples\" 虚拟目录，并在 URLScan 中屏蔽对 .asp 示例文件的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0738.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0738","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0738.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0738.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-92vg-86x4-j5qj/GHSA-92vg-86x4-j5qj.json","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/752a0e2467403295006418f2de0b0dcb65d62426/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0738.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88076/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0356.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0357","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0357.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0739","title":"Microsoft Internet Information Server 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 及 Site Server 附带的 codebrws.asp 示例文件存在访问控制缺失漏洞，远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可通过直接向该示例文件发送特制 HTTP 请求，利用其对文件路径参数缺乏充分校验的缺陷，读取服务器上任意文件的内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，仅影响系统机密性，CVSS v2 评分 5.0，中危等级。Microsoft 已发布安全公告 MS99-013，建议删除或限制对示例文件的访问以完成修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0739"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.393","remediation":"删除 IIS 服务器中 `/IISExamples` 及 `/IISSamples` 目录下的 `codebrws.asp` 等示例文件，或直接卸载 IIS 示例组件。对于无法删除文件的场景，可在 IIS 管理器中限制 `.asp` 脚本映射或通过 NTFS 权限拒绝对示例目录的读取访问。","status":"completed","