权限提升。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.3 版本，攻击者需拥有本地账户，无需其他特殊条件即可利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1079"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.653","remediation":"升级至 AIX 5.1 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。IBM 已针对此问题发布 APAR IX84149，建议安装对应补丁。如无法升级，可通过限制 ptrace 系统调用的用户权限（仅允许 root 用户使用）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92601792420088&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93587956513233&w=2","http://www-1.ibm.com/servlet/support/manager?rs=0&rt=0&org=apars&doc=08E0B1A1B85472A1852567C90031BB36","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/439","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1079.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1079.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1079","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1079.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1079.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1079.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qpvh-wpmg-5vw6/GHSA-qpvh-wpmg-5vw6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--64058aab-083d-4dce-afe1-93ac7b4f3bdb.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000627.txt"],"